   <abstract>This postcard has Hank McCauley sitting on a railing playing a guitar. Recto reads: To my good Friends Hank McCauley. Verso reads: Howdy Folks: I'll be singin' to you over WMT and KWCR every Mon. Wed., and Fri. at 12 noon and on KWCR Tues. and Thurs. at 8:30 P.M. I sure hope you'll be listenin' and don't forget my sponsors, The Hamilton Seed and Coal Co. recleaners and shippers of Hawkeye Brand Farm Seeds. Addressed to C. H. Snyder.</abstract>
